<div class="container">
  <%- include('../partials/headernav', {pageTitle: "Home"}) %>
</div>

<body>
  <main>
    <div class="container border-bottom">

      <div class="px-4 text-center" id="front-hero">
        <img id="front-logo" class="d-block mx-auto mb-4" src="img/logo_new.png" alt="">
        <h1 class="fw-bold text-body-emphasis mainHead">Guerrillas of Liberation</h1>

        <div class="col-lg-6 mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-3">
            <abbr title="Established 2003" class="initialism">est. 2003</abbr>
          </p>
          <p class="lead mb-5 scaleText">
            An international Arma community with over 20 years of experience!
          </p>

          <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-sm-flex justify-content-sm-center" id="frontButtons">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4 gap-3"><a href="/discord">Join Us!</a></button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg px-4 btn-secondary"><a href="/about">About Us</a></button>
          </div>
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col arma-logos-main">
                <img src="img/a3_logo.png" alt="ArmA3"/>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col arma-logos">
                <img src="img/ar_logo.png" alt="ArmAReforger"/>
                <img src="img/a2_logo.png" alt="ArmA2"/>
                <img src="img/acwa_logo.png" alt="ArmACWA"/>
                <img src="img/opf_logo.png" alt="OperationFlashpoint"/>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      </div>

      <div class="container px-4 py-5 border-bottom" id="featured-3">
        <div class="row g-4 py-5 row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3">
          <div class="feature col">
            <div
              class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
              <!-- <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em"><use xlink:href="img/calendar.svg"></use></svg> -->
              <!-- <img class="" width="50px" height="50px" src="img/calendar.svg" alt=""></img> -->
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2">Weekly Operations</h3>
            <p>We conduct operations every Sunday night at 5pm GMT and Thursday night at 7pm GMT.<br>Our missions are
              created in-house using our own framework built over decades of work and our missions also put an emphasis on realism, action and narrative.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature col">
            <div
              class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
              <!-- <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                <use xlink:href="#people-circle"></use>
              </svg> -->
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2">Dedicated Servers</h3>
            <p>Our dedicated game and TeamSpeak servers are available 24 hours a day for our members to have a chat or play
              some games together. The use of our game servers for games other than ArmA is permitted for any interested
              members.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature col">
            <div
              class="feature-icon d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center text-bg-primary bg-gradient fs-2 mb-3">
              <!-- <svg class="bi" width="1em" height="1em">
                <use xlink:href="#toggles2"></use>
              </svg> -->
            </div>
            <h3 class="fs-2">Modifications</h3>
            <p>We use various mods from the community including ACE and TFAR during our operations to enhance the
              experience. We have a large customised framework for our Arma 3 missions that enhance gameplay.</p>
            <a href="#" class="icon-link">
              Check out our Modlist >
              <svg class="bi">
                <use xlink:href="#chevron-right"></use>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="container px-4 py-5 border-bottom mb-5" id="icon-grid">

        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-lg-4 g-4 py-5">
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#bootstrap"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">Recruitment Period</h3>
              <p>For any new member joining us, they will initially join as a recruit. After completing 2 operations of each type (Thursday & Sunday), they are promoted to a full time member starting at private.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#cpu-fill"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">Non-Restrictive Ranks</h3>
              <p>The main purpose of ranks are to reflect a member's experience and knowledge, nothing more. Everyone has a voice, regardless of rank.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#calendar3"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">No One Faction</h3>
              <p>We utilise all kinds of factions and nations that the Arma platform has to offer. Playing the same faction over and over can be come tedious, so we offer a good handful such as: US, UK, Germany, Latvia, Finland, Sweden, Norway, Czech, RU, as well as many independent factions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#home"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">No One Composition</h3>
              <p>As well as a variety of factions. We train for all kinds of compositions, such as, Motorised, Mechanised, Special Forces, Air Assault and Basic Infantry Squads.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#speedometer2"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">Dedicated Training</h3>
              <p>In order for our members to be familiar with both technical and tactical knowledge, we have dedicated trainings on a vaariety of subjects.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#toggles2"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">International Unit</h3>
              <p>Despite the fact that over half of our member base is from the UK. We still have a large portion of members that come from all over europe and further.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#geo-fill"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">Basic ACE Medical</h3>
              <p>Tired of watching a black screen for 15 minutes because you got ArmA'd? Well we certainly are. Which is why we've cranked the dial back on the the medical system, making it simpler and easier to get back into the fight.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col d-flex align-items-start">
            <svg class="bi text-body-secondary flex-shrink-0 me-3" width="1.75em" height="1.75em">
              <use xlink:href="#tools"></use>
            </svg>
            <div>
              <h3 class="fw-bold mb-0 fs-4 text-body-emphasis">Editing & Extras</h3>
              <p>We also host editing sessions for those interested in exploring ArmA 3's 3DEN editor. For missions made that are of good quality, we'll also add them to our rotation!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

